{"tid":248169,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"理性詳細分析香港連鎖餐廳，文長慎入！歡迎大家探討下","createTime":"2017-05-18T10:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T12:57:49.000Z","uid":90,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3a303b001ddd0c0ebbbbf176d76311ecb74804","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"大家食J 》》》》》 all<br />\n無需多講...."},{"pid":"5af951a66f780c105f35a2e3d918fd5f3bef0297","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒，初初見到大家食J間咁嘅舖頭，仲有個濕鳩軍佬LOGO已經覺得好撚核凸<br />\n成浸大陸味出晒嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入都唔撚想入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我今日可以企係度同大家講，大家食超晒譚仔班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁而家未hit，未有咁多人食，質素仲keep到嘅時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拿拿聲帶條女入去食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請認清楚大家食J 嘅logo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/317Q27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F317Q27.png&h=fb515997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k49582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk49582.jpg&h=1a52c973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招牌嘢梗係手攪麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手攪麵簡直係大家食J嘅代名詞<br />\n揀完麵底跟住就揀餸<br />\n屌你老味嚟到大家食J唔食過山雞真係唔好話自己嚟過唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定係過山雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點睇湯底，湯湯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你問我，譚仔湯底同大家食J湯底比，邊個好啲<br />\n我會答你屎水同神仙水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基於大家食J個湯底實在太撚正<br />\n我奉勸各位食大家食J 一定要揀豆卜<br />\n豆卜係神仙水湯底裡面浮浮沉沉<br />\n吸收晒神仙水嘅仙氣<br />\n一啖咬落去就有如咬落精緻嘅灌湯餃一樣<br />\n濃厚嘅湯底加上豆卜嘅質感<br />\n有得輸咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後當然係嘢飲<br />\n嘢飲梗係凍檸茶啦<br />\n檸檬嘅酸味同糖嘅甜味仲有紅茶嘅澀味融為一體<br />\n你識揀啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n譚仔？收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家見面大家食<br />\n大家食面見大家</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"5191d8b9887f5155bb520219b58cb761cc783103","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"過山雞，聽聞呢味菜係呂先生人生第一次玩過山車時諗出來既食過山雞尤似坐過山車時而平穩，時而刺激過山雞外層略脆味濃刺激味覺神經內裡肉質鮮嫩多汁味道穩健充實每次食過山雞必然回想起人"},{"pid":"0f4ae33641b25032a930abfafc306deae05e32e4","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"男人大丈夫<br />\n<br />\n就算只係一次都好<br />\n<br />\n應該去試下食大家食<br />\n<br />\n除左醫肚外感受下一間食店<br />\n<br />\n老闆開舖既心血，熱誠<br />\n<br />\n好多年輕人怨天尤人，嘆今時今日時不我予，工作毫用心<br />\n<br />\n但你請睇下一個無學歷（斗膽假設，講錯我會道歉）既大叔靠雙手打拼出來既成就<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生有好多比年輕人學習既地方<br />\n<br />\n去大家食食一餐食飽之餘，體驗下成功既要領"},{"pid":"6f2f43e88ac6881528d771fc03f619f2b76eab77","tid":248169,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"巨b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98614b9e5b536d68924de6042932144563299efd","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"我個人推薦 茄蛋湯底手攪麵過山雞"},{"pid":"d341eedd9afa3d6b947d924e731b8a714e9acbed","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巨b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693f04759a2595aeb82ab5c47ed93f159d068e06","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家食最正係果兜辣菜甫<br />\n</span></span><br />\n大家記得要一個<br />\n免費嘅！"},{"pid":"23014807421aac71f140228853b23911ed86f54e","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"呂以村先生既才能遠超肯德基伯伯<br />\n<br />\n肯德基伯伯淨係識整雞<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生才華洋溢識整手攪面，村村住家窩面，過山雞，滷大腸，十三會<br />\n<br />\n求其一種都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n相比肯德基淨係識整雞 <br />\n<br />\n而呂以村先生38歲就創立大家食<br />\n<br />\n肯德基呢？<br />\n<br />\n六七十歲先周街搵人比錢佢開舖"},{"pid":"acae6906cd7d710f31bab5b09ae54ea1385e9f91","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"而我認為除非譚仔同佢三哥聯手<br />\n<br />\n否則呂以村先生單打獨鬥下必輕取二人<br />\n<br />\n單單一招大絕手攪面<br />\n<br />\n兩個譚食出盡全力都無法招架"},{"pid":"5501ca5edb6cbe74f7ecf8afc9ac2da4e13f903f","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"呂以村先生贏過食神挑戰賽第二<br />\n<br />\n你可能話，點解贏唔到第一？<br />\n<br />\n因為呂先生既大絕手攪面當年仲未完成<br />\n<br />\n如今呂先生既手攪面已經獨霸美食界<br />\n<br />\n每條面都用捕獲等級4200既奇蹟小麥精製<br />\n<br />\n手攪面以呂先生既80G臂力攪成其QQ程度無法抗拒<br />\n<br />\n每條面，充滿熱血男人之情"},{"pid":"7a4ff31e403eee39d92525cea69ba37530cc6f8f","tid":248169,"uid":64143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"冇咗呢句嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFAQ: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 食過一次，勁撚難食。<br />\nA:</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWfO0C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWfO0C.png&h=87e4e240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa70a4136a4e969c8cfab6e453d432e520ed0403","tid":2481