h.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F192120_75c8230330180bf39a9cd5dc56d20d77.jpg&h=6c3081fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/192121_9c2b8ff5535125aa59aa1da64f610f04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F192121_9c2b8ff5535125aa59aa1da64f610f04.jpg&h=4f4eb73a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/192125_844fe49fb04c052657578aba7d6dbb4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F192125_844fe49fb04c052657578aba7d6dbb4a.jpg&h=b45825a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/192129_b87cb0091664c77af0c5bfca7989bebe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F192129_b87cb0091664c77af0c5bfca7989bebe.jpg&h=c841bc7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7f679ec8e35b61799278e42362c6e3b5b20fb6b","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:23:20.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】將軍澳隧道公路，昨凌晨發生四車連環相撞。以平價手打作招徠的「大家食」連鎖店東主呂以村，駕駛私家車途中遇上車禍，與另外三車連環相撞。意外中呂以村及一名的士司機受輕傷，平治跑車司機驗出酒後駕駛，但無超標被警員口頭警告。<br />\n昨凌晨1時許，呂以村（38歲）駕駛一部豐田 Camry私家車，沿將軍澳隧道公路慢線往觀塘方向，駛至電訊盈科電話機樓對開時，因前車慢駛，呂相應減速時，尾隨一部載有兩名男子的平治 CLK23O跑車，即時扭向中線企圖閃避，結果撞向沿中線駛至載客的士。<br />\n平治跑車與的士相撞後衝回慢線，再撞向呂以村私家車車尾，而的士亦同時失控衝過快線，被另一部駛至的士撞向右車尾。<br />\n意外中，呂以村頭部不適，中線的士姓余（52歲）司機亦頸及雙腳受輕傷，車上乘客無恙。兩名傷者送院敷藥後無大礙。平治跑車姓張（33歲）司機接受警方酒精測試，證實酒後駕駛但未有超標被警告。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6484ed1b0298afef1f2bca445b75d208af59c7a","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】連鎖店「大家食」位於九龍城食品工場昨午發生火警，工人烹煮食物時，懷疑火舌燒油槽內的油，起火並冒出大量濃煙，消防員到場疏散20多人，開喉灌救將火撲熄。東主呂以村被灼傷但拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n 店東呂以村救火時右手被灼傷。　資料圖片<br />\n店東呂以村救火時右手被灼傷。　資料圖片<br />\n工場油煙槽燒<br />\n首宗意外現場在九龍城馬頭角道40號東南工廠大廈3樓一間食品公司的工場，為連鎖店「大家食」工場。昨午1時許，工人在廚房煮食物，懷疑爐火旺盛向油煙槽燒，油煙槽因積有大量油，即時燒，冒出大量濃煙，38歲東主呂以村救火時被灼傷右手。<br />\n消防員接報到場，疏散工場七名工人及大廈十多名職員，在工場內開喉灌救，約10分鐘後將火撲熄，消防員調查火警原因無可疑，受傷的呂以村在現場接受敷治後拒絕送院。<br />\n呂以村出身傳奇，1992才由汕尾新豐移民來港，努力學廚，至1998年在深水開了第一間店後，憑拼勁越做越有成績，以手打馳名飲食界，店越開越多，還將自己容貌作為店舖生招牌。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈機！"},{"pid":"b307590d60bc3ee127b38265499b199fe974d060","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呂生真心屈機"},{"pid":"8b29be0f940ae1ac1a983897ef98e01586ba3c1a","tid":248169,"uid":58375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"金槍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恐龍頭骨湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6a57362343b628c4739e3ebb42658e5ed559a2","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金槍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恐龍頭骨湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/193221_052ccb5a57a5be2c614fb8c6069bffdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F193221_052ccb5a57a5be2c614fb8c6069bffdb.jpg&h=54ce771a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35a9deaed3c543f314f753c70932679e2f75bdef","tid":248169,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"呂茂正先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c26a737e1349ca707be0219d3ec04d6fd19699","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呂茂正先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家食的創辦人為呂以村（已改名為呂茂正）[2]。呂原為廣東省汕尾海豐人[3]，1993年移民初來到香港，第一、二份工作都在食肆任職，從雜工做到大廚；其後，轉為自己做老闆，在薄扶林道香港大學附近，推木頭車賣炭燒的雞蛋仔。1998年，他看中港人喜歡吃麵條，便用賣雞蛋仔賺來的二十多萬積蓄，在深水埗福榮街開設了首間大家食[4]。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0373c2a7fa01ccbeffe1404313f37c71073c57","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"蔡瀾推薦香港最好餐廳之一<br />\n新城電台第四屆食神爭霸戰銀獎<br />\n2011TVB飲食天王"},{"pid":"da9955de1a579ab84ae672280b54ebf87ea969bb","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"2009年，集團以1,920萬元購入葵涌打磚砰街華基工業大廈地下作為總公司地址[6]。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該食店目前有八間分店：<br />\n<br />\n九龍城譚公道分店<br />\n旺角上海街分店<br />\n旺角花園街分店<br />\n佐敦上海街分店<br />\n深水埗福榮街分店<br />\n深水埗汝州街分店<br />\n荃灣路德圍分店<br />\n旺角旺角道分店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意！"},{"pid":"eedeb3004040c9a2d8da7f666fe548961fe50e33","tid":248169,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"巨b我睇完你寫嘅打之後好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8f17c3f9d5ae0e926d7cb2c13fdb5cd2ac77d2","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"「一次不試您錯過，二次不來我過錯。」[1]<br />\n「一家做麵大家食，大家食麵碗碗香。」<br />\n「用心創出美味送菜，用手搞出條條好麵。」<br />\n「大家見面大家食, 大家食麵見大家。」<br />\n「大家食有金槍人。」<br />\n「大家食J」先係正貨。"},{"pid":"5c1f393139094b4f2c28a44de70f3d00f86d84e3","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"撚手名菜<br />\n<br />\n削搖麵<br />\n手攪麵<br />\n蕃茄牛肉麵<br />\n村村住家鍋麪（飲食天王至尊榮譽得獎主食菜式）<br />\n村村蔬果冰<br />\n過山雞"},{"pid":"938215e2fdd30775a698b1f5cdfa96bb12cb9b3d","tid":248169,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"豬肚冬菇手攪麵次次必嗌"},{"pid":"9987df4c8f9eb77ab6fe4b663219666ed1720cf8","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巨b我睇完你寫嘅打之後好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好嘢嚟<br />\n茄蛋湯底 手攪麵 過山雞 <br />\n再免費要個辣菜甫"},{"pid":"adf53e84f3b9ae252b4d739fcc8b7fe9572a3585","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬肚冬菇手攪麵次次必嗌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識食"},{"pid":"ec26a6fcce6d009f5d58da4ca513da8435b63932","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/193730_aba3ad366c8fccc812f5f66e9553355c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F193730_aba3ad366c8fccc812f5f66e9553355c.jpg&h=757e622a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5942930c184ab73d9e8b611775be3598a562614f","tid":248169,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豬肚冬菇手攪麵次次必嗌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識食</blockquote><br />\n絕椒肚，幾撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475f31e55414b77598fbbee4145c5708f5a1ad9e","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>豬肚冬菇手攪麵次次必嗌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識食</blockquote><br />\n絕椒肚，幾撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過山雞 狀元骨<br />\n全部都好型"},{"pid":"556f6d21d17bf012f835430ee408aa4772d930f5","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"大家食飲食集團（以下簡稱大家食）於1998年8月由呂茂正先生創立，呂先生在創立大家食之前曾任職待應、廚師，也曾在香港區以木頭車賣&quot;雞蛋仔&quot;，眼見港人喜愛麵食便毅然創立了&quot;大家食&quot;。憑著呂先生不斷努力與堅持，大家食由開業時一間舖發展到現在有7間分店了 ! 更憑著創意和對自我的要求，獲得第四屆食神爭霸戰銀獎、飲食天王創意手攪麵天王獎等多個飲食獎項。<br />\n大家食一向追求創新，選用上等材料，即叫即製，務求使我們的顧客享受到真正的飲食樂趣。我們透過不斷的改進，力求做到精益求精，改善我們的服務及食物水準，把我們製作的美食帶到每個家庭之中，為每個家庭增添快樂與滿足。"},{"pid":"4af38d532ca9fb136cc0273c2eb0b768a22034ba","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"我們的文化：<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n大家食一直保存著深厚獨特的文化，這種文化能夠帶領我們將最好的服務質素給予每一位顧客，同時這種文化能夠令員工之間更團結、積極、上進。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 以禮待人<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們深信以禮待人是本公司最重要的文化之一，亦是我們同事之間的溝通模式。以禮待人的精神能夠使我們的員工提供最親切的服務給顧客，也能令到員工之間更加融洽及有效率。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 不批評、多讚揚<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n呂茂正先生認為批評別人只會帶來壞處，被批評的人會覺得不愉快及影響工作情緒，相反多些鼓勵別人更可以增加公司每一位員工的動力。所以公司常常鼓勵及讚賞員工，希望員工能有愉快的心情工作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n 守信、盡責、勇於承擔<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n為顧客帶來信心的食物是我們對每一位顧客的承諾。從開業到現在，我們堅守信念，不停為顧客設想，務求顧客能夠感受到真正「大家食」的感覺。呂茂正先生多年來不斷作出新嘗試，亦為自己已創下的食物一再改良，盡心盡力地為每一位顧客出力。"},{"pid":"0cae83c6d1546d6d6de05dc75b947bd501628ed2","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.eattogether.com.hk/index_topic.php?did=183047&amp;didpath=/183047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eattogether.com.hk%2Findex_topic.php%3Fdid%3D183047%26didpath%3D%2F183047&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5593c4b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eattogether.com.hk/index_topic.php?did=183047&amp;didpath=/183047</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277735f64d79776d5001b681214f768e54110015","tid":248169,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"樓主識嘢！ Ho ball！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0c02d1ebffe1c9013e53fec990a5766c81ed42","tid":248169,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:44:12.000